{
  "stem": "1413.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He put us away in a corner that nobody would see us doing nothing all day long in wintertime, only to have us back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If he got better paid that we did good work, and all that kind of work, because we were not interested in working for them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But since I did it to his satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One day, the wagon broke down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had to break up pipes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were skin and bones, all of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the wagon broke down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't deliver the goods that night, because they worked 24 hours there in that-- I got the name here, [INAUDIBLE] working in Blechhammer.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so the next morning, he said, I will get you for that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You didn't-- at me-- you didn't do what you're supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we worked two weeks before we get one Sunday off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We work Saturday and Sunday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And so instead of giving us a wagon, he gave us a heavy pipe to carry on our shoulders, the small fore, and the back ones in the back.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was the boss of that group, let's say seven, eight, nine people, whatever it was, how many you need.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he told us, you don't get a wagon today, on a Sunday, on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You've got to carry it on your shoulders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were skin and bones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So let's say I walked in the middle, because I always worked with the people, even though I was not-- I couldn't-- the boss saw us carrying on our shoulders the pipe.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He pulled me, he pulled me out under the pipe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have to carry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
